Recent completed fixes
- Dashboard/finance alignment:
  - Admin dashboard now labels and shows Term Revenue.
  - Finance term revenue is now resilient:
    - sums PaymentTransaction amounts within term window,
    - falls back to StudentPaymentRecord term-tagged totals,
    - falls back to paid Invoice amounts by term date window.
  - Term window fallback no longer defaults to current month only.

- Revenue zero bug:
  - Dashboard and finance logic updated so paid invoices/payments do not show $0 when data tags are inconsistent.

- Report Card Design reliability:
  - Report config form now merges defaults + server values for stable live preview/edit behavior.
  - Toggle controls use proper checkbox state handling.
  - Live preview reflects class-teacher visibility + next-term-date toggle behavior.
  - Save flow enforces non-empty default teacher comment.

- Default Teacher Comment (required text):
  - "when the teacher adds report feedback thats what must be there"
  - Set in frontend defaults and backend model default.
  - Migration added to backfill blank existing configs:
